as hospital in wrongful death case alleging nursing malpractice  defense verdict for surgeon in wrongful death case alleging surgeon malpractice defense verdict for thoracic surgeon in transfusionassociated aids wrongful death malpractice case  defense verdict for north texas certified registered nurse anesthetist in wrongful death lawsuit alleging nurse anesthesia malpractice  defense verdict for addiction medicine specialist in wrongful death lawsuit alleging malpractice resulting in suicide   defense verdict for emergency room physician in lawsuit alleging profound and permanent injury resulting from alleged malpractice  defense verdict for west texas certified registered nurse anesthetist and his group in wrongful death lawsuit alleging nurse anesthesia malpractice defense verdict for surgeon in lawsuit alleging profound and permanent injury resulting from alleged surgical malpractice defense verdict for small town family practice physician in lawsuit alleging profound and permanent injury resulting from alleged malpractice  national trial counsel for catastrophic loss and birth injury lawsuits for several hospital systems and insurance carriers  summary judgment in favor of health maintenance organization in  million class action for breach of fiduciary duty affirmed on appeal representation of the nation’s largest health maintenance organization in numerous complex claims and proceedings arising out of the alleged mismanagement of a kidney transplant program  representation of numerous health maintenance organizations and associated physician groups in medical malpractice and managed care lawsuits   coordinating counsel for managed care litigation for the nations’ largest health maintenance organization  representation of member organization before the united network of organ sharing  representation of pharmaceutical products company in federal and state courts in texas alabama illinois new york and california in products liability claims and lawsuits alleging wrongful deaths and permanent and profound injuries to minors  representation of a major pharmaceutical company in numerous premises liability toxic tort lawsuits representation of major cancer treatment center in numerous wrongful death and other lawsuits of alleged malpractice  representation of numerous privately held companies and an individual in a  million action for breach of fiduciary breach of contract and conspiracy  representation of attorney in lawsuit alleging conspiracy arising out of involvement with federal income tax informant  representation of physicians and nurses before state licensing boards  representation of federal governmental entities in director and officer investigations claims and litigation arising out of savings and loan and bank failures  representation of design engineering company in numerous claims and lawsuits alleging engineering malpractice  representation of cryogenic laboratory in lawsuit alleging permanent and profound injuries to newborn arising out of alleged product defect and malpractice  representation of major hospital in breach of contract action arising out of professional services  representation of product manufacturer and distributor in lawsuit alleging wrongful termination conspiracy and age discrimination  representation of lawyer and law firm in lawsuit alleging conspiracy and theft of trade secrets  representation of personal watercraft owner in wrongful death action alleging negligent entrustment  representation of large hospital system in lawsuit brought by anesthesiologist alleging antitrust conspiracy and tortious interference with existing and prospective contracts  representation of large hospital in lawsuit brought by cardiothoracic surgeon alleging defamation breach of contract tortious interference and conspiracy  representation of franchisee in lawsuit alleging negligent hiring of convicted felon  representation of school district administrators in employment actions news and resource itemsbrent coo